acp-agent-protocol.skill - Agent Control Protocol for OpenClaw

STATUS: ACP CLI available but acpx runtime plugin missing
ACTION NEEDED: Install acpx plugin and configure API keys

Quick test:
1. Check status: python3 skills/acp-agent-protocol/scripts/check_acp_status.py
2. Install acpx: npm install -g @openclaw/acpx (if available)
3. Set API key: export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-key
4. Test: openclaw acp client

Current limitation: "ACP runtime backend is not configured" error when trying to spawn ACP sessions.